dc_description_s: This point data layer represents addresses for Milwaukee County, Wisconsin in 2017. It is a feature class within the geodatabase Milwaukee_Addresses_2017. [points representing locations of addresses - points are placed within the parcel with which an address is assocated - when possible, points are placed within the footprint of the building with which an address is associated - when a parcel or building is associated with multiple addresses, multiple points will be placed within each parcel or building.]
uw_supplemental_s: Augmented original metadata with UW-Madison specific elements.For complete metadata documentation, please visit https://county.milwaukee.gov/EN/Administrative-Services/Land-Information-Office/GIS-Data-Downloads.This data was submitted to the UW geospatial archive in 2018. Content may be considered current as of December 31, 2017. It was published to the UW geospatial archive as part of the Wisconsin Department of Administration Land Information Program annual collection of public data for the year 2018.
